text: The Östra Torp Church () is a church building in Smygehamn in Sweden. I belongs to the Källtorp Parish of the Church of Sweden. It was inaugurated on 14 June 1911. It replaced an older church which had been destroyed by a fire in 1909. The church is the southernmost in Sweden. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Church of Sweden churches
title: Östra Torp Church
